snippet.title: Find a Subscription Box for Grown Up with Amber Rose
snippet.description:
YAY, our very first episode of Stuff My Box presented by NOM NOM Boris and Nina. We are a silly duo of Gay Foodie and Female Metal Vocalist who buy subscription boxes and try them on each other. Anything from adult toys to make up. Our goal is to try each box multiple times to honestly know if its worth your money. We are just starting out and still learning things, so please bear with us.

For our first episode, we are trying an amazing Slutbox by Amber Rose. https://myslutbox.com
